brand.name: Natural Selections
brand.description:
The power of better flower lies in a better cultivation process; that’s why we don’t use unnecessary and excessive interventions to produce our plants. All our flower is slowly dried at low temperatures to best preserve cannabinoids and terpenes, and we hand inspect and trim every flower prior to packaging. It’s just part of our nature. Our indoor farms house a bank of 2,600 seeds representing over 60 breeders and more than 225 strains. By leveraging our robust seed bank and genetic pool, we regularly cultivate, test, and share new strains to continually explore the best that nature has to offer.

We’re good at what we do because we love what we do. We’re cultivating a community who appreciate the beauty of the natural world around us. We’re plant experts meticulously monitoring our cultivation environment to bring out the best of nature for those who appreciate it most. You deserve flower the way flower was meant to be. Our unique, tried and true strains are cultivated in harmony with nature for both healing and happiness. Tune in to the Natural Selections variety show of color, aroma, and flavor, where it’s all good, naturally.
